== Isesengura ==
''A Stab in the Dark'' hamwe n’ibikurikira bizwiho kwibanda ku buhemu bw’abagabo nk’isoko y’amakimbirane yo mu miryango, igikoresho cy’umugambi kidakunze gukoreshwa muri sinema yo muri [[Gana]] na [[Nigeriya]]. 

== Kwakira ==
''A Stab in the Dark'' hamwe nibisobanuro byayo bifatwa nkibimwe mubikorwa byiza bya Quarshie.  ''A Stab in the Dark'' yatsindiye amafaranga  kandi yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi, harimo na FIlm nziza muri ibihembo bya Gana Movie Awards mu 2000.
